### 3. **VC-LLM-Research-Guide.md** (30 pages, Your Research Coordinator)
**Purpose**: Maps your 4 LLM subscriptions to specific research work, with synthesis workflow.

**LLM Assignments**:
- **Claude Code**: Technical architecture, database design, algorithm design, security, testing, monitoring (16 prompts)
